      "text": "The code is still there. It's still complex, but you don't live in it anymore."
    },
    {
      "start": 5.14,
      "end": 11.76,
      "text": "You live in the specification. The code is generated, verified, and if needed, regenerated."
    },
    {
      "start": 13.36,
      "end": 14.8,
      "text": "Heather just spread case."
    },
    {
      "start": 15.68,
      "end": 19.7,
      "text": "So here's the mental shit. You don't patch socks because socks got cheap."
    },
    {
      "start": 20.32,
